and above suÔ¨Écient level of component supply;
‚Ä¢ choice of the current margins for the given products.
The strategical decisions may concern the choice of the storage management strategy (for example ATO, MTO or
the increase/decrease of the stock level), level of the margin of proÔ¨Åt and used prediction techniques.
In this paper we are focusing on the analysis of the inÔ¨Çuence of the level of the margin for the Ô¨Ånal product and
the choice of the prediction method of the customer demand. The strategy manager module should select the proper
actions to be executed and their conÔ¨Ågurations.
